relationships.description: United States conducted a military intervention against Venezuela, including a blockade and strikes.
U.S. Army Delta Force executed the extraction mission on Venezuelan soil.
Delta Force captured Nicolás Maduro during the raid.
Delta Force captured Cilia Flores alongside Maduro.
US forces captured Maduro and charged him with narco-terrorism.
US forces captured Cilia Flores and charged her with narco-terrorism.
Donald Trump is the President of the United States.
Trump ordered the military intervention that captured Maduro.
Maduro was the President of Venezuela.
Cilia Flores is the First Lady of Venezuela.
Cilia Flores is the wife of Nicolás Maduro.
UN Security Council held an emergency session regarding the intervention in Venezuela.
UN Security Council deliberated on the US military intervention.
FANB is the military force of Venezuela.
FANB was the target of US bombardments.
Vladimir Padrino López is the Defense Minister of the FANB.
Padrino López condemned the US strikes as a violation of sovereignty.
Fuerte Tiuna is located in Caracas.
Fuerte Tiuna is the headquarters of the FANB.
Caracas is the capital city of Venezuela.
Miranda is a state in Venezuela.
Aragua is a state in Venezuela.
La Guaira is a state in Venezuela.
La Carlota is an airfield located in Caracas.
El Volcán is a communications hub in Venezuela.
USS Iwo Jima is a US warship.
Maduro was transported on the USS Iwo Jima.
Cilia Flores was transported on the USS Iwo Jima.
New York is a city in the United States.
Southern District of New York is a federal judicial district in the US.
Maduro is indicted in the Southern District of New York.
Cilia Flores is indicted in the Southern District of New York.
Pam Bondi is the US Attorney General.
Bondi confirmed charges against Maduro.
Cartel of the Suns is a Venezuelan organization.
Maduro is implicated in the Cartel of the Suns.
Cilia Flores is implicated in the Cartel of the Suns.
PDVSA is the state-owned oil company of Venezuela.
China is a major trading partner of Venezuela, specifically for oil.
María Corina Machado is an opposition leader in Venezuela.
Edmundo González Urrutia is the president-elect of Venezuela.
Machado and González are working together in the transition plan.
Delcy Rodríguez is the Vice President of Venezuela.
Colectivos are pro-regime groups in Venezuela.
Colectivos support the Maduro regime.
Guri Dam is located in Venezuela.
Colombia is a neighbor of Venezuela.
Brazil is a neighbor of Venezuela.
Gustavo Petro is the President of Colombia.
Petro condemned the US intervention.
Lula is the President of Brazil.
Lula condemned the US intervention.
Russia condemned the US intervention.
Cuba condemned the US intervention.
Argentina celebrated the US intervention.
Javier Milei is the President of Argentina.
Milei celebrated the US intervention.
EU expressed caution regarding the US intervention.
UK stated it was not involved in the intervention.
Keir Starmer is the Prime Minister of the UK.
France criticized the US intervention.
Christopher Landau is the US Deputy Secretary of State.
The Caribbean Sea is adjacent to Venezuela.
US naval operations occurred in the Caribbean Sea.
Orinoco Belt is a region in Venezuela.
Zulia is a state in Venezuela.
Monagas is a state in Venezuela.
Bolívar is a state in Venezuela.
Spain granted asylum to Edmundo González.
Darién Gap is a migration route used by Venezuelans.
